# Stack Baseline

Use pnpm, TypeScript strict, TanStack Start/Router, React, shadcn/ui + Tailwind,
SurrealDB, Dexie IndexedDB caches/drafts/future saves, Vitest, Playwright,
Biome, Docker, and Dokploy. No npm/yarn, ESLint, Prettier, Redux, Zustand, real
club/player names, or localStorage game state/cache/drafts.
